Abstract = {As more people start using the Internet and more content is placed
   online, the chances that individuals will encounter inappropriate or
   unwanted adult-oriented content increases. This paper presents a
   practical and scalable method to efficiently detect many adult-content
   images, specifically pornographic images. We currently use this system
   in a search engine that covers a large fraction of the images on the
