   Tzeng, Jung-Ying, N Carolina State Univ, Bioinformat Res Ctr, Raleigh, NC 27695 USA.
   Tzeng, Jung-Ying, Natl Cheng Kung Univ, Dept Stat, Tainan 70101, Taiwan.},
