   Hussein, Mohamed Abdrabou, King Fahd Univ Petr \& Minerals, Interdisciplinary Res Ctr Adv Mat, Dhahran 31261, Saudi Arabia.
   Hussein, Mohamed Abdrabou, King Fahd Univ Petr \& Minerals, Dept Mech Engn, Dhahran 31261, Saudi Arabia.},
