   Akpa, Onoja M., Univ Memphis, Sch Publ Hlth, Div Epidemiol Biostat \& Environm Hlth, Memphis, TN 38152 USA.
   Aderinto, Nicholas, Ladoke Akintola Univ Technol, Dept Med \& Surg, Ogbomosho, Nigeria.
