   Sacayan, Redeemtor R., Mindanao State Univ, Iligan Inst Technol, Coll Sci \& Math, Dept Math \& Stat, Iligan 9200, Philippines.
   Gulam, Sacaria B., Mindanao State Univ Main Campus, Coll Informat \& Comp Sci, Dept Comp Sci, Marawi 9700, Lanao Del Sur, Philippines.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.sasc.2025.200352},
EarlyAccessDate = {JUL 2025},
