   Van Wyk, Jan, Univ Pretoria, Fac Vet Sci, Dept Vet Trop Dis, Onderstepoort, South Africa.
   Shapiro-Ilan, David, US Dept Agr, Agr Res Serv, Fruit \& Tree Nut Res, Byron, GA USA.
   Kannan, Govind, Auburn Univ, Dept Poultry Sci, Auburn, AL USA.},
