   Storage management; Classification algorithms; Distributed learning;
   large datasets; SVM; classification; distributed processing; distributed
   storage},
Keywords-Plus = {SUPPORT VECTOR MACHINE},
Author-Email = {er.amritkabir@gmail.com},
Number-of-Cited-References = {44},
