   Ahmad, Fahad, Univ Portsmouth, Portsmouth Artificial Intelligence \& Data Sci Ctr, Portsmouth, England.
   Alanazi, Saad Awadh, Jouf Univ, Coll Comp \& Informat Sci, Dept Comp Sci, Sakaka, Aljouf, Saudi Arabia.
