Month = {NOV 10},
Abstract = {A modulation classification method in combination with partition-fractal
   and support-vector machine (SVM) learning methods is proposed to realize
   no prior recognition of the modulation mode in satellite laser
   commu-nication systems. The effectiveness and accuracy of this method
   are verified under nine modulation modes and compared with other
   learning algorithms. The simulation results show when the
   signal-to-noise ratio (SNR) of the modulated signal is more than 8 dB,
   the classifier accuracy based on the proposed method can achieve more
   than 98\%, especially when in binary phase shift keying and quadrature
   amplitude shift keying modes, and the classifier achieves 100\%
   identification whatever the SNR changes to. In addition, the proposed
   method has strong scalability to achieve more modulation mode
   identification in the future.},
