Abstract = {An understandable classification models is very useful to human experts.
   Currently, SVM classifiers have good classification performance;
   however, their classification model is non-understandable. In this
   paper, we build DRC-BK, a decision rule classifier, which is based on
   structural risk minimization theory. Experiment results on UCI dataset
   and Reuters21578 dataset show that DRC-BK has excellent classification
   performance and excellent scalability, and that when applied with MPDNF
   kernel, DRC-BK performances the best.},
