   Qin, Jushuang; Chen, Zhibo; Lu, Hao; Cui, Xiaohui; Wang, Zhenyao; Mou, Chao; Fan, Guangpeng, Natl Forestry \& Grassland Adm, Engn Res Ctr Forestry Oriented Intelligent Proc, Beijing 100083, Peoples R China.
   Qin, Jushuang; Chen, Zhibo; Lu, Hao; Cui, Xiaohui; Wang, Zhenyao; Mou, Chao; Fan, Guangpeng, Hebei Key Lab Smart Natl Pk, Beijing 100083, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jag.2025.104874},
