   Chikabvumbwa, Sylvester, Catholic Univ Malawi, Dept Geog \& Environm Studies, Montfort Campus,POB 5452, Limbe, Malawi.
   Mwase, Weston; Kathewera, Msaiwale, Lilongwe Univ Agr \& Nat Resources, Bunda Campus,POB 219, Lilongwe, Malawi.
